data.description:
Discover the ideal blend of convenience and comfort in this 3-bedroom gem located just 5 minutes from the Cleveland Zoo. A quick 13-minute drive takes you to downtown, while Hopkins airport is only 11 minutes away.

Step inside to find a thoughtfully designed interior, with a spacious master room featuring a luxurious jacuzzi for ultimate relaxation. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for family, guests, or a home office.

Outside, a well-manicured yard provides space for outdoor activities. This residence combines suburban tranquility with city proximity, creating the perfect home for a balanced lifestyle.
